decision_conditions:
CONDITION:  Details in respect of the following shall be submitted to and approved in writing by the Council as Local Planning Authority in consultation with English Heritage before the relevant work is begun.  The relevant work shall be carried out in accordance with such approved details:

a)  full schedule of fittings including chimney pieces, doors (and door furniture), windows, mosaic floors
     etc. affected by works to be provided prior to works beginning on site;
b)  detailed drawings of new single glazed sash windows at 1:20 scale;
c)  detailed drawings of new doors at 1:20 scale;
d)  detailed drawings at 1:20 scale and 1:1 scale of retained and altered court room fittings.

REASON:  In order to safeguard the special architectural or historic interest of the building.
